RACE.RACE_TEXT: TURFWAY PARK RACE 1 1M All Weather Track CR: 74. Maiden Claiming Purse 25000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 120 lbs. Claiming Price $15,000, For Each $2,500 To $10,000 1 lb.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SAN MARCO CITY lagged back to the half, rallied with a run in upper stretch, kept on in the final furlong and prevailed at the wire. PRINCE OF ROSES sharp speed from the gate, clear to quarter pole, battled in the final stages but lost the head bob in a game effort. CONNECT ME raced along evenly to the stretch run, battled on gamely to wire for the show spot just missing the place award. DOMHNALL chased pace to quarter pole but gave way in the stretch run. COUNT MY DREAMS good position to the half but could not keep up and wilted far back in the stretch run.

ENTRY.OWNER: Southwest Racing Stables Inc and Triple V Racing LLC
ENTRY.COMMENT: sharp speed from the gate clear to quarter pole, lost head bob

ENTRY.COMMENT: raced along evenly to the stretch run, battled on gamely to wire

ENTRY.COMMENT: good position to the half, could not keep up and wilted back

ENTRY.COMMENT: chased pace to quarter pole, gave way in the stretch run

ENTRY.NAME: San Marco City
ENTRY.COMMENT: lagged back to the half, rallied with a run in stretch prevailed
